<div class="hero-banner">
  <h1 style="color:white !important">RDK for Home</h1>
  <p>
    RDK (Reference Design Kit) is a flexible, scalable open-source platform standardizing the development of broadband, video, and connected devices for service providers and manufacturers. Deployed on over 150 million devices globally, its widespread adoption drives next-generation digital experiences, fostering innovation and efficiency in video, broadband, and IoT applications.
  </p>
</div>
