    <h2 style="text-align: center;">Connectivity</h2>
    <p style="text-align: center;">
      Framework that powers broadband gateways, modems, and routers, enabling high-speed internet delivery for service providers. It provides a standardized platform with built-in Wi-Fi management, device diagnostics, and network optimization, streamlining advanced broadband service deployment, improving operational efficiency, and ensuring consistent performance.
    </p>
